{"tid":1830114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有野想講","createTime":"2020-01-19T10:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T10:48:05.000Z","uid":315301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a91d7c618f4c9d081b62d3b7cfebe90747446dc0","tid":1830114,"uid":315301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"小弟愚見<br />\n<br />\n1. 要承認其實黨鐵係最好，因為狗冇得 set roadblock，同埋係邊個站出有更大彈性，亦容易混入人群<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果要拉人過欄杆，最好捉手腕，會減少跣手風險 (野外定向老師教)<br />\n<br />\n3. 撤退期間無需撚狗，倒不如留翻啖氣跑<br />\n<br />\n4. 撤退期間最好唔好開遮，會阻住其他人，尤其係快速撤退嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n5. 港島真係唔適合大型集會，難去難走，好似今日咁只要係金鐘、中環、海傍佈防，隨時可以大圍捕"},{"pid":"7ca1ff37a0cd57ac931887af51228e5ca75d9dba","tid":1830114,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"【跪求】twitter要人！今日集會好多外媒有報，但無人推！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1830108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1830108</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=ea0c794d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"4bdfd8f2d1bea3219fd07917ffc012abd6890cb7","tid":1830114,"uid":315301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c308753f84a5031d87075b7b7c2a7f8f52f9595","tid":1830114,"uid":149